These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: d&b, hip-hop, salsa, pop, house, electronic
6 different pets are kept: horse, ferret, frog, fish, lizard, snake
 1. the fan of salsa is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
 3. the fan of house is not the owner of the lizard##6
 4. the fan of pop is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
 5. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
 6. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
 7. the owner of the lizard is not the fan of hip-hop##6
 8. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of d&b is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the fan of pop##7
10. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
11. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
12. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
13. the owner of the horse is the fan of d&b##1
14. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the fan of house##5
15. the fan of electronic is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | d&b | salsa   | electronic     | hip-hop    | house   |
| Pet           | lizard | horse   | snake | fish | frog | ferret |

