.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: animation, martial-arts, mystery, satire, crime, superhero
6 different pets are kept: bird, horse, hedgehog, goldfish, lizard, rabbit
 1. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
 3. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
 4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 5. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
 7. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
 8. the person watching animation movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching crime movies is not the owner of the lizard##6
10. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the goldfish##7
11. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the person watching crime movies##5
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
13. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
14. the owner of the rabbit is in an even position##4
15. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
16. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
17. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the person watching crime movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | superhero | satire | crime     | mystery      | animation |
| Pet           | horse         | hedgehog        | lizard   | goldfish | bird | rabbit    |

