.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, sprite, almond-milk, iced-tea, 7up
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: skateboarding, rowing, sailing, soccer, snowboarding, 7up-polo
 1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
 4. the person who's sport is rowing is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
 5. the person drinking juice is not the person who's sport is skateboarding##6
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is 7up-polo##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking mirinda##7
11. the person who's sport is 7up-polo is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
13. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
14. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is 7up-polo##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | iced-tea        | almond-milk | 7up    | juice    | sprite | mirinda |
| Sport      | rowing | snowboarding  | 7up-polo | soccer | skateboarding | sailing      |

