The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: scientific, musical, spy, comedy, disaster, martial-arts
 1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 3. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is not the person drinking tea##6
 6. the person drinking coffee is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person drinking tea##7
 7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking juice##7
 8. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 9. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking fanta##7
10. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
11. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
12. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
13. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking fanta##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
| Beverage      | fanta | milk | juice | coffee | tea | sprite   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy  | comedy      | scientific | disaster     | martial-arts | musical |

