.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: hiking, singing, board-games, writing, reading, woodworking
The people have 6 different jobs:  manager, teacher, dancer, chef, mechanic, paramedic
 1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
 2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the dancer##5
 4. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the chef and the teacher##7
 5. the paramedic is on the left or right of the dancer##3
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the mechanic##1
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
 8. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
 9. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
10. the teacher is somewhere to the right of the paramedic##5
11. the paramedic is on the right of the dancer##1
12. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
13. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
14. the teacher is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
15. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Hobby   | board-games         | writing | singing | hiking   | woodworking | reading  |
| Job     | mechanic | chef  | dancer  | paramedic | teacher  | manager |

 